&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://sgcafe.com/2017/09/kemono-friends-website-releases-statement-regarding-director-tatsukis-removal-kemono-friends-movie-delayed/&#34;&gt;Kemono Friends website releases statement regarding director Tatsuki&#39;s removal, Kemono Friends movie delayed - SGCafe&lt;/a&gt; : 海外の反応&lt;/p&gt;
